         <div type="traslation">
            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>On the Jovian year Piṟapava, month
               of Cittirai, 13th day, the day of Saturday, under the constellation of Uttiram,
               twelfth [lunar day], lakkaṇam of Riṣapa, the handwriting (kayyeḻuttu) of Laṣcumaṇaṉ
               son of Muṉiyappaceṭṭiyār copied and fully completed the Kācikāṇṭam.</p>
         </div>
